{"tid":2423744,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股災殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避","createTime":"2021-02-26T05:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:40:23.000Z","uid":143878,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c76dcc96247ecc830503deaf42bf63f53ec6788a","tid":2423744,"uid":143878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"睇到個股市嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照講比佢聽，睇左顏色跌幾多%都未開始睇，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「股災殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；股災殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街美股真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"24b41449c774b6b5c185c2f9b3aa326090e130e4","tid":2423744,"uid":121291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663e572bb21bb9de567af1a98a22fa90f351d981","tid":2423744,"uid":143878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24b41449c774b6b5c185c2f9b3aa326090e130e4","tid":2423744,"uid":121291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"股災殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；股災殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&he